tip_battle.title: Odin (Argent)
tip_battle.message:
• -When granted Thunderous Blessing, damage dealt to the enemy increases, and damage dealt by the enemy decreases.
  • -The enemy has resistance to all damage, and physical attacks also deal reduced damage.
  • -The enemy's Rage level is more likely to increase when his remaining HP is between 80% and 90% or 40% and 50%.
  • -While infused with the power of earth, the earth damage you deal to the enemy increases.
  • -The enemy uses Trine on heroes not infused with the power of earth to Paralyze them, ignoring resistances.
  • -The enemy uses Death to Instantly KO all targets in range, ignoring resistances.
  • -The enemy uses Mighty Guard to grant itself Protect, Shell, and Haste.
  • -The enemy uses Lightning Zanokuken and Antiheal, which reduce the effects of healing.
  • -The enemy uses Argent Zantetsuken to Sap, ignoring resistances, with an effect that depends on its Rage level.
  • -At Rage level 3, Argent Zantetsuken will KO the entire party.
  • -If the fight lasts too long and you haven't reduced the enemy's HP enough, the enemy uses Argent Warp to remove all heroes from the battle.
  • -After a certain number of turns passes, or when the enemy loses a certain amount of HP, its Rage level increases up to a maximum of 3.
  • -When the enemy's Rage level increases, it takes less damage and deals more damage.
  • -Deal damage greater than the damage cap to lower the Rage level by 1.
